seo: Spring Cloud Function, SPEL表达式注入漏洞, 漏洞检测, 安全测试
seo_en: Spring Cloud Function, SPEL Expression Injection Vulnerability, Vulnerability Detection, Security Testing
summary: 该插件用于检测目标主机是否存在Spring Cloud Function SPEL表达式注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload并验证DNSLog反馈来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the target host has Spring Cloud Function SPEL Expression Injection Vulnerability by sending a specific payload and verifying the DNSLog feedback to confirm the existence of the vulnerability.
